{
  "stem": "6523.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It's, uh,  maybe a couple--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hm?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Smashed into the other, because in the outside, [? they pushed in. ?] It's cold.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like a fire, [INAUDIBLE] get out the fire.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] from over there-- this was in Gross-Rosen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How they got from over there, the same group, what he got in [INAUDIBLE] in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He make up the Schindler's list.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He got us to Gross-Rosen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "From Gross-Rosen, he guarded us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He keep us all of them together-- the same whole group.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is the reason we came alive and we finished alive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The-- this was the-- the [? event ?] of Schindler.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I can finish up here, [INAUDIBLE], not to bring you--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just tell me now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Gro-- you're in Gross-Rosen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're all jammed together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They disinfected you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Gross-Rosen, they called us in German, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[GERMAN]-- how are you going to say [GERMAN]?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Uh, temporarily you-- you are going in transport temporarily.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In transit.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You are.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why did you know how-- [LAUGH] a transit came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We go direct to Brunnlitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Over there-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got to get Edith.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She's going to tell you about this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I've got to tell you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Is I wouldn't separate from her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Is what she's doing in Plaszow, we know it's a transport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she know where I go, and she liked to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How is she go just the men?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Crazy.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She dressed herself a man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she got into this transport.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Somehow you get killed, you get beaten.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You've got-- somehow, you don't ask question.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "How she got-- she got in in this transport.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The trouble was after a while, I don't know, this woman transport was canceled.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she went back to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she couldn't go with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
